# {{ project_name }}

> {{ project_description }}

This project was generated from [OpenProductKit](https://github.com/ravipurohit1991/OpenProductKit) — a white-label product-template built around one decoupled core with thin web / CLI / desktop adapters.

## Run it

```bash
uv sync --dev
uv run {{ cli_name }} dev              # API on http://127.0.0.1:8000
{%- if include_web_frontend %}
pnpm install && pnpm -C apps/frontend dev
{%- endif %}
{%- if desktop_framework == 'pyside6' %}

# desktop app (native Qt widgets over the same core, no web build):
uv run {{ cli_name }} desktop
{%- elif desktop_framework != 'none' %}

# desktop app (same core, no HTTP server):
uv run {{ cli_name }} build web && uv run {{ cli_name }} desktop
{%- endif %}
```

## Serve these docs

```bash
uv run {{ cli_name }} docs serve       # http://127.0.0.1:8001
uv run {{ cli_name }} docs build       # static site in ./site
```

